Title: Continuous reinvention: A brief history of block storage at AWS
Description: Marc Olson, a long-time Amazonian, discusses the evolution of EBS, highlighting hard-won lessons in queueing theory, the importance of comprehensive  instrumentation, and the value of incrementalism versus radical changes.
